(19, 2581, 'Melisa', 'Melisa@gmail.com', '', '180.178.145.28', '2018-03-13 10:49:35', '2018-03-13 10:49:35', 'Came here on vacation and my husband really needed a hair cut and a shave - started looking online and got worried he was going to go into one of these places where you have to pay like 300 dollars. he found Stellar and was pleasantly surprised. The ambiance was great. The Custer service was excellent. And the cut and shave were perfect. Best hair cut and shave he had. The only complaint I have is there\'s not a shop in my hometown in Ohio. Look forward to coming back!', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
(20, 2591, 'Alex', 'Alex@gmail.com', '', '180.178.143.22', '2018-03-12 13:40:43', '2018-03-12 13:40:43', 'Came in with high expectations, left 100% satisfied. Jamie was knowledgeable, informative, and skilled with not just cutting my hair, but also explaining the why on specific styling and maintenance techniques. If you want someone who truly knows what they are doing, I would recommend', 0, '1', '', 'listing', 0, 0),
